{"tid":114152,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"靴里拉警告列強小心曼聯","createTime":"2017-02-09T14:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T06:41:13.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"06637e425952a071f17d8a2683de8143dd179321","tid":114152,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images.performgroup.com/di/library/goal_uk/33/e3/manchester-uniteds-most-expensive-transfers-of-all-time-ander-herrera_1don1u4ix0zc81jnf7mouaizof.jpg?t=147208982&amp;w=620&amp;h=430\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.performgroup.com%2Fdi%2Flibrary%2Fgoal_uk%2F33%2Fe3%2Fmanchester-uniteds-most-expensive-transfers-of-all-time-ander-herrera_1don1u4ix0zc81jnf7mouaizof.jpg%3Ft%3D147208982%26w%3D620%26h%3D430&h=0f8fe228&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曼聯中場安達靴里拉警告英超前5強小心紅魔鬼，因為下半季曼聯將會捲土重來。<br />\n<br />\n摩連奴領導的曼聯現在於英超排名第6位，但在24場比賽之後，只落後次席的熱刺5分。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯已經在聯賽連續15場不敗，靴里拉指前5列強都會留意到曼聯的回勇表現。<br />\n<br />\n「聯賽前6隊加上愛華頓，這7支球隊的競爭非常激烈。大家都想打入前4，不過我認為曼聯現在處於一個非常理想的時刻。前5球隊都知道曼聯正在追趕上來了。」靴里拉說。<br />\n<br />\n靴里拉對上兩季都入了9球，不過今季上陣21場都未入球，一直在尋找入球。靴里拉說：「每個人都想幫球隊入球，我也會努力嘗試。我會盡力爭取入球的，記得首季起腳8次便入了8球，但有時你命中目標，有時不會，足球就是這樣的了。」下輪比賽，曼聯將在周六鬥屈福特。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=b84cddff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"2301182eabf8f6b07b74ed4ba8c129aa13ea7283","tid":114152,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:21:33.000Z","msg":"易食指數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5eae405e9992650f0029bc54efcda24ee605d5","tid":114152,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:22:21.000Z","msg":"改文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df54beaec829d0b9a0a392583a420808fb1f468","tid":114152,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:22:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n派膠球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad2c903175465a1633fcd0eadc9da297e6004d00","tid":114152,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:23:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>改文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n堅過石堅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ce30e6ab82d82fee3d414cfee5218a7e5feb876","tid":114152,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:39:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8329a373bc63b3b188ca1be084db34573162d3","tid":114152,"uid":2033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:41:19.000Z","msg":"致命靴里拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f0b931cbcc5c3a5524ec61be3e149c1966f0067","tid":114152,"uid":54747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:04:31.000Z","msg":"京京了"},{"pid":"841492b6f834f162555ab92195b5aa2bf3e0042c","tid":114152,"uid":872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:06:33.000Z","msg":"蛇仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1a0f75b8528b1bc589176267ffd64af60fcc79","tid":114152,"uid":15886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T18:28:45.000Z","msg":"警告！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0e5c648b2a153dc63b3f4601d834017ddec803","tid":114152,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T18:36:27.000Z","msg":"除左令神奇隊長38秒拎紅牌仲識啲咩"},{"pid":"3cd916782fccd80fe5e3225de1a2c5b8d66ebd61","tid":114152,"uid":37566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T20:05:53.000Z","msg":"又有新警告王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3d377c37884caa7cfe1858cf04eba6f48fa079","tid":114152,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T20:51:50.000Z","msg":"厹"},{"pid":"9724daaa1c463896ad8c479675bae3577189e23c","tid":114152,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T22:12:53.000Z","msg":"感情台"},{"pid":"07a00e6705f4495a450fc8852feb668a10dd01f0","tid":114152,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T03:31:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>感情台</blockquote><br />\n🐶"},{"pid":"481f1b4ca4de7f1b2977d03ae1963c2491620a9e","tid":114152,"uid":4052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T03:34:25.000Z","msg":"小心曼聯會笑死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b05009f990b8fc5095e1820f24e506f0194e7818","tid":114152,"uid":4846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T03:50:39.000Z","msg":"今週升上第5啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f65c040e35aca6b4a748f04b753e4f635c5a43c","tid":114152,"uid":34542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T03:52:41.000Z","msg":"好撚京京啊"},{"pid":"e2bf8852ed837c798de10cc72cb8f9c82a1e4a70","tid":114152,"uid":1848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T03:53:57.000Z","msg":"【咖喱篇】今周傾乜：英超4哥睇好邊隊？<br />\n利物浦上場威到盡，大炒同市宿敵愛華頓4粒，繼續坐穩第4位。今季個勢咁好，唔通紅軍有機入前4，踢歐聯？唔好咁老定住，小心曼聯殺上嚟！<br />\n曼聯𠵱家差利物浦6分，都係兩場波嘅差距啫，紅魔有機會追得番。紅魔本身前場好手眾多，就算莫耶斯只靠兩翼傳中嘅落後戰術，靠朗尼同尹佩斯嘅個人能力，都足以贏唔少醜陋嘅勝仗，就好似季初贏水晶宮2:0嗰類。<br />\n不過，衰就衰在佢兩位喺上半季成日受傷，搞到曼聯冇人負責埋門一腳，更令到對方唔驚曼聯嘅鋒線，夠膽壓前攻曼聯。𠵱家朗尼同尹佩斯已經出返嚟，佢兩位健健康康的話，絕對有力幫曼聯搶分！<br />\n睇咗一場桑馬達，覺得佢幾啱曼聯，一嚟已經適應咗英超，即插即用，二嚟佢雖然係攻中，但喺曼聯雙翼齊飛嘅體系入面，都做到貢獻。以莫耶斯嘅能力，小弟唔會寄望佢喺今季內可以轉變踢法，以桑馬達為核心踢中路進攻；但小弟有啲信心，佢可以利用桑馬達去改進佢雙翼齊飛嘅戰術。桑馬達長傳準，喺中路分邊同埋轉方向嘅能力唔錯，可以用傳球幫翼鋒搵空位。如果莫耶斯用得好，路爾斯華倫西亞同艾舒利楊格嘅威脅會更加大。<br />\n不得不提一點，下半季發力係莫耶斯嘅傳統，過去幾季，佢以前帶嘅愛華頓都係漸入佳境，越近季尾越踢得好。文：咖喱"},{"pid":"bf5938550c29d2996fabe3135e937979b546bab3","tid":114152,"uid":37566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T06:41:13.000Z","msg":"Be careful man u ar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}